description: Inpatient Encounter Well Newborn care, SNOMED CT, Created for NDNQI pressure ulcer and risk measures.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The clinical focus of this measure is the inpatient well newborn.),(Data Element Scope: Using the Quality Data Model, this data element will map to "Encounter."),(Inclusion Criteria: The newborn whose inpatient care was in the normal newborn nursery.),(Exclusion Criteria: Outpatient care before and after birth such as prenatal education, well child visits and home visits. Also excluded are Inpatient Neonatal Intensive Care Nursery Level II, III and IV.)
